1. Install Node.js (LTS). Close and reopen your terminal after install.
2. Verify install:
```
node -v
npm -v
```

3. download the zip file:
```
1. download it and after download extract the file
2. open folder and click on above header like This PC > (C:) > <something> > in that type CMD and click enter 
```

4. Install packages:
```
npm install
```

6. Start dev server:
```
npm run dev
```

7. Open the app or website at:
```
1. after npm run dev command it will show on link looks like this <http://localhost:5173>
2. ctrl press link will open - http://localhost:5173
```

8. Stop the server when needed: press Ctrl + C in the terminal.


